NMF in Many Parts(2)

The number of things going on in this picture is at least double what you think it is. And then there’s all the things that happened that night that aren’t in the picture. A couple good rock bands, a hillbilly jug of sangria, a foamy (but free) keg, etc. etc. If I sat here and actually listed everything, you’d get bored and never read again. You had to be there. And you should have.
